<p>Alesha demanded: 'Bring back the crab! I was willing Olaf down because last time we saw you, you were going crazy which was so funny, but you didn't do that tonight.'</p>

<p>Loving it: Ashley said: 'It should be jarring but the transitions are so seamless. The whole panel was vibing, a classical orchestra making me bop my head - I love it!'</p>

